  OrderIdx: 4
  Title: "D\u1EA4U \u1EA4N & T\u1EF0 H\xC0O"
  HexCode: 0x3B
  Content:
  - "V\u01B0\u01A1n t\u1EA7m kh\u1ECFi v\xF3c d\xE1ng qu\u1ED1c gia, sinh vi\xEAn
    UIT \u0111\xE3 nhi\u1EC1u l\u1EA7n g\xE1nh v\xE1c tr\u1ECDng tr\xE1ch \u0111\u1EA1i
    di\u1EC7n Vi\u1EC7t Nam, kh\u1EB3ng \u0111\u1ECBnh b\u1EA3n l\u0129nh tr\xED
    tu\u1EC7 t\u1EA1i c\xE1c s\xE2n ch\u01A1i h\u1ECDc thu\u1EADt ________ h\xE0ng
    \u0111\u1EA7u nh\u01B0 ACM-ICPC hay Olympic Tin h\u1ECDc."
  - "S\u1EF1 k\u1EBFt tinh gi\u1EEFa nh\u1EEFng gi\u1EA3i th\u01B0\u1EDFng c\xF4ng
    ngh\u1EC7 danh gi\xE1 v\xE0 v\xF4 s\u1ED1 c\xF4ng tr\xECnh nghi\xEAn c\u1EE9u
    t\u1EA7m c\u1EE1 c\u1EE7a sinh vi\xEAn \u0111\xE3 b\u1ED3i \u0111\u1EAFp n\xEAn
    b\u1EE9c tranh r\u1EF1c r\u1EE1, ph\xE1c h\u1ECDa nh\u1EEFng ________ \u0111\xE1ng
    t\u1EF1 h\xE0o c\u1EE7a UIT tr\xEAn ch\u1EB7ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng c\u1ED1ng
    hi\u1EBFn."
